I made the slaw from this recipe and loved it! I used 1/2 cup mayo and 1/4 cup fat-free yogurt but almost the whole amount of chipotle.

Rating: 4
With a couple additions/changes, I rate this a four. Used sour cream instead of mayo and adobo sauce instead of chipotle powder. Added lime juice to sauce. Grilled a poblano pepper and used pepper strips as garnish. Used avacado as garnish as well. Absolutely loved it.

