As quick and easy as these were, I thought these tacos were awesome!

Rating: 3
Like other reviewers, I found it wanting in something more. I made the slaw with buttermilk instead of yogurt, squeezed in some lime juice, and used chipotle sauce from adobo peppers in place of the powder. Yum! I also added some frozen corn kernels to the slaw.

